description:
The unnamed Einzbern Master is the Master of http://anidb.net/ch40363 [Avenger] in the Third Holy Grail War mentioned in Fate/hollow ataraxia and the Master of http://anidb.net/ch88727 [Ruler] in the Third Holy Grail War of the Fate/Apocrypha universe.
Source: TYPE-MOON Wiki
name: Einzbern Master
